OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 30 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1986FBBC Two's striped '2' ident airs
OL,7,Ffor the final time in the early
OL,8,Fevening.
OL,9,
OL,10,FIt would be replaced by a new
OL,11,Fwhite/red/green/blue ident, featuring
OL,12,Fembossed 'TWO' lettering.
OL,13,
OL,14,FThe new ident is believed to have aired
OL,15,Ffor the first time at 7.15pm (TBC).
OL,16,
OL,17,FThe new clock would not be seen until
OL,18,Fclosedown, at 1.05am on 31st March
OL,19,F1986.
OL,20,
