OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 30 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1997FChannel 5 begins broadcasting at
OL,7,F6pm, from 33 transmitters.
OL,8,
OL,9,FIt would be the UK's final national
OL,10,Fanalogue television service.
OL,11,
OL,12,FTim Vine and Julia Bradbury present the
OL,13,Flaunch show.
OL,14,
OL,15,CG2001FBBC Choice Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fceases broadcasting.
OL,17,
OL,18,FThe service would be replaced by the
OL,19,Fnational version of the channel.
